description: ConfuserEx 2 is a open-source protector for .NET applications. It is the successor of Confuser project and the ConfuserEx project.
releaseNotes: The development is currently in alpha stage. While the features of the original ConfuserEx are implementedand working, the features that are part of the new version 2.0 are still in development and may not yield the desired results.
